title: Esther Quintana Salinas
text: Esther Quintana Salinas (born 1 July 1951) is a Mexican politician affiliated with the <a href="National%20Action%20Party%20%28Mexico%29">PAN</a>. She served as Deputy of the <a href="LXII%20Legislature%20of%20the%20Mexican%20Congress">LXII Legislature of the Mexican Congress</a> representing <a href="Coahuila">Coahuila</a>, and previously served in the LVIII Legislature of the <a href="Congress%20of%20Coahuila">Congress of Coahuila</a>.
